'''盧維隆沙河'''（'''Ruvyironza River'''）是[[非洲|非洲]]的河流，是[[尼羅河|尼羅河]]最偏遠的源頭<ref>[http://www.egyptattraction.com/nile-river-egypt.html Africa Longest River | Egypt Nile River | World Longest River | Nile White | Ancient Capital Nile<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710173134/http://www.egyptattraction.com/nile-river-egypt.html |date=2011-07-10 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761558310/nile.html |title=Encarta online encyclopedia |access-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513133842/http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761558310/Nile.html |archive-date=2008-05-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，河道全長約100公里，發源自[[布隆迪|布隆迪]]海拔高度2,400米，在[[基特加|基特加]]東北方注入[[魯武武河|魯武武河]]。其後經[[坦桑尼亞|坦桑尼亞]]注入[[卡蓋拉河|卡蓋拉河]]<ref>[https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.geocities.com/bourbonstreet/5809/discover/nile.html&date=2009-10-25+13:49:18 NILE]</ref>，再流進[[維多利亞湖|維多利亞湖]]。

